The copyrighted work in question is the following text appearing on http://iphonehelp.in/2009/12/25/apple-owns-islate-com-since-2-years/

"I am not really suggesting that the upcoming 7”³ Apple TabletMac would be called the iSlate, but Apple owning the domain is certainly a indication that this was something Apple considered important to its business. Unlike iPhone.com which Apple bought for a huge $ amount as they had not secured it before announcing the iPhone in 2007, this time they are justified in securing possible names for products underdevelopment."
